| Name       | Description                          | Params                         |
|:-----------|:-------------------------------------|:-------------------------------|
| `execute`  | Called when the module is executed.  | `Mollitia.Circuit` **circuit** |
| `state-changed`  | Called when the breaker state changes.  | `Mollitia.BreakerState` **state** |

